title.narrative:
An annual review is organized by senior MoH management to analyze UCP-FE and EPI performance on data programmatic and financial data basis.Quarterly DGS's monotoring and coordination meeting is organize to support and track all DRS, health Programs performance. setting up an entrenched culture in the DGS, EPI and DRS of strategic data collection and use through dashboards. 
DGS/MoH's Standard Operation Procedures and organizational chart of UCP-FE are validated by at least 2 external donors as able to manage all health external funding with a focus in Gavi accelerated Transition period for immunization; 
Two Advocacy meetings organised by DGS in collaboration with private sector for mobilization of domestic resources through the Government, civil society and the private sector for immunization.
